 Shift your weight to your left hand as you turn your body to the right; bend your right leg behind you and extend your right arm up.", "eccentric": "Return to the center and repeat on the opposite side.", "concentric": "Continue, alternating sides.**Make it easier:** Don’t raise your arm after you bend your leg behind you.**Make it harder:** Balance with your arm and leg extended for two counts."}'::jsonb,
